  "riddle": "1. Unearth the tale of a man who scaled the peaks of the volleyball world, winning gold for his national team — how many shining medals graced his achievement at the World Championships?\n\n2. Contemplate the name of a composer whose melodies have enchanted many. How many prestigious awards has this maestro from the film industry claimed throughout his celebrated career?\n\n3. Seek out the nation that dances to the diverse rhythms of its people — what is the current count of souls living under the sun in this vibrant land?\n\n4. A singer of great renown hails from a city where devotion intertwines with melody. In which city, and in this case, which nation, did he first see the light of day?\n\n5. Hot on the trail, guide your gaze toward the capital of this land of rhythms; perched high above sea level, how far does the ground rise in meters?\n\n6. As you wander through the streets, discover the spiritual landmarks that frame the skyline. What number of churches can you find within proximity of the bustling metropolitan expanse?\n\n7. Combine your discoveries: add the elevation from clue 5 to the church count you unveiled in clue 6. What is the result of this union?\n\n8. A curiosity resides within the name of the birthplace you unearthed in clue 4. To reveal its secret, find the position of its first letter within the alphabet—what numerical value does this yield?\n\n9. A journey towards an ancient site awaits. Look up how high the earth rises in this subdistrict known for its history and remnants; what is its elevation?\n\n10. To finalize your quest, calculate the result of: the absolute difference between the heights from clues 5 and 6, then take that number modulo 10. What single digit emerges from this arithmetic?",
